  <h4>Orientation</h4>

  <p>A popover has four orientations depending on where it needs to be located, <strong>top</strong>, <strong>right</strong>, <strong>bottom</strong>, or <strong>left</strong>. If a popover overlaps critical content or is cut off by the edge of the screen when triggered, change the orientation.</p>

